  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A model revision was issued in early 2026 to incorporate updated impeller tip-clearance geometry and revised blood rheology constants; however, the primary experimental dataset used to calibrate model inputs retains a vintage from late 2025 and has not yet been superseded. Re-validation against the updated dataset is described as planned but has not been executed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels fall at or below required levels consistent with MRL 5 expectations.",
