    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package on the basis that Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification bounds hemolysis predictions below the clinical NIH threshold at 4 of 5 operating points and that the single exceedance at the high-speed low-flow condition is within engineering judgment for a Low assurance level submission. All 13 credibility factors were assessed; achieved levels are below required levels across the board, consistent with MRL 5 expectations and a Low assurance designation. Re-validation of model inputs against post-February 2026 revision data is planned for Q2 2026 and is noted as an open action item. The team judged the current evidence sufficient for a Not-for-final-approval submission stage.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
